item.title: I downloaded this server and some reason when i make a profle it saves but
item.dc:creator: @The_Web_Guy The Web Guy
item.description:
@The_Web_Guy wrote:

Please don’t put more than half your question in the subject box. The subject box should be something like, “Login problems.”

Anyways, what do you mean you can’t log back in. Usually with login problems there is an error message associated with the problem. When you click login does it say…

a) Your account is already logged in.
b) Error Connecting to Server.

Provide more information and I can try to help you. I’m assuming it’s saying your account is already logged in, so to trouble shoot I would restart the server and see if you can log in, if you can, and everything saved… Then this sounds like a problem with the server fully not deregistering the player. If that’s the error you’re getting, let me know and I’ll tell you what methods to post.
